snippet: A St. Louis County woman denied that she posted a claim that grand juror told her the panel lacked evidence to prosecute the Ferguson police officer who fatally shot 18-year-old Michael Brown.
abstract: St Louis County woman Susan M Nichols denies she posted on Twitter a claim that grand juror told her the panel lacked evidence to prosecute Ferguson police officer Darren Wilson, who fatally shot 18-year-old Michael Brown; says her account was hacked.
lead_paragraph: A St. Louis County woman denied that she posted a claim that grand juror told her the panel lacked evidence to prosecute the Ferguson police officer who fatally shot 18-year-old Michael Brown.

headline.main: Missouri: Woman Denies Grand Jury Leak
headline.print_headline: Missouri: Woman Denies Grand Jury Leak
